  %h1 What is JLibPam?
.right
  %p
    JLibPam is a small java library that allows you to access the PAM
    security layer of your Operating System.
  %p
    Using jlibpam is easy.  To authenticate a user on the system
    you need to run:
        
  :plain
    {coderay::java}
    Pam.authenticate("system", "user", "password");
    {coderay}

